\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

, the image space triangle having height 
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

 and base 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

, is similar to the object space triangle having height 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 and base 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

